extendedInfo.description: GW CarPix offers you world's finest cars and motocycles collections with weekly update! You can browse and download 45,000+ high quality car + motocycles wallpapers for free. All the car and gear photo and backgrounds are downloadable. Features:- Browse over 45,000+ Car, Tuners, Motocycles, Bike wallpapers, Gears and backgrounds- Download and save car wallpaper- Sory by freshness and download times- Exact size preview (scrollable wallpapers)- Well organized 3 levels Categories / Sub categories.- Keyword searching for the whole car library- Share car wallpaper to facebook, twitter, SMS.- Small (fast speed) or Large (high quality) thumb viewing.- Fast and stable server connection.Our application is free, fast and offers the best collection of popular, HOT and high resolution car wallpapers and backgrounds with DAILY UPDATES!We put much afford to categorize the wallpapers into a well define 3-level 4,000+ categories, including the major manufacturer and tuner:1) Car ManufacturerAcura, Alfa Romeo, Aston Martin, Audi, Benz, Bentley, BMW, Ferrari, Fiat, Ford, Gemballa, Honda, Land Rover, Lexus, Porsche, Rolls Royce, Saab, Shelby, Volkswagen...2) Car TunersAC Schnitzer, Alpina, Arash, Arden, ART Tuning, BF Performance, Brabus, Carlsson, Carrozzeria Touring Superleggara, DMC, Edag, Edo Competition, Endora, Steinmetz, TechArt, Wheelsandmore, Zagato3) EventsGrand Prix Formula One4) Bike / MotocycleBMW, DN-01, Ducati, Honda, Kawasaki, KTM, Suzuki, YamahaDesktop site: www.gwallpaper.com
